      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "yet not like David his father; not with a perfect heart, with that sincerity and uprightness as he did, see 2 Chronicles 25:2, ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "yet not like David his father; not with a perfect heart, with that sincerity and uprightness as he did, see ",
