        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "yet not like David his father",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "] The Chronicler merely gives ‘but not with a perfect heart’, making no mention of Amaziah’s resemblance to Joash, nor of his falling short of David.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
